Name: Dawn Break -Origin-

When the Day of Eclipses arrived, a dark shadow appeared, and from the sky, a mysterious lady descended. Never a dull moment when playing this action-RPG. In order to conquer the Boss, all you can do is to challenge and practice continuously! ◎An epic adventure journey with large numbers of campaigns. There’re over hundreds of levels, including “Normal” and ”Elite” mode waiting for you to play.
